3rd_Rock_from_the_Sun http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/3rd_Rock_from_the_Sun 0 3rd Rock from the Sun is an American sitcom television series created by Bonnie and Terry Turner, that originally aired from January 9, 1996, to May 22, 2001, on NBC. The show is about four extraterrestrials who are on an expedition to Earth, the third planet from the Sun, which they consider to be a very insignificant planet. The extraterrestrials pose as a human family to observe the behavior of human beings. 3rd Rock from the Sun is an American sitcom television series created by Bonnie and Terry Turner, that originally aired from January 9, 1996, to May 22, 2001, on NBC.
